./COVERAGE.md:510:| [`org.jetbrains.kotlin:kotlin-stdlib-common`](https://github.com/JetBrains/kotlin) | 1.5.31<br>– 2.4.0-Beta2 | 100% (0/0 calls) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Kotlin Standard Library Common provides the platform-independent portion of Kotlin's standard library for multiplatform projects. It supplies common APIs and core language support that are shared across Kotlin/JVM, Kotlin/JS, and Kotlin/Native.</details> |
